cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with image deblurring using deep learning techniques and gyroscope measurements. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of gyroscope measurements also suggests that it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics), as it involves sensor fusion and motion estimation. The use of deep learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.GR (Graphics).
